snippet.title: Best VGM 297 - Castlevania: Order of Ecclesia - Tymeo Mountains (Jaws of a Scorched Earth)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2008 - https://youtu.be/calW24ddgOM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Castlevania: Order of Ecclesia
Jaws of a Scorched Earth
